title: Still haven't received my rewards.
body: Even though I contacted riot support, I have not received my rewards yet. I ended up this season diamond V and I haven't gotten any bans or chat restrictions.{{item:3070}}

replies.body: As mentioned on the [EUNE Status Page](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune), we're having some issues on this region with certain players. We're working on a fix, but I don't have any ETA on when that will roll out. Since you've submitted a ticket already, feel free to address any further questions about this to your specialists on your ticket.
Yes, a submitted a ticket because that is what many of you guys told us to do. Thank you very much for your reply
